00:50:07,166 --> 00:50:10,333
And also men should understand that they must

694
00:50:11,000 --> 00:50:13,208
every day spend some time with their children.

695
00:50:13,208 --> 00:50:15,083
This is extremely important,

696
00:50:16,000 --> 00:50:17,291
because children are so relaxing.

